Class Viewer

  • java.lang.Object
    • view.Viewer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Observer, ViewerCenterBoard

    public class Viewer
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Observer, ViewerCenterBoard
    The Viewer class allows to draw rectangles on a specified canvas. It implements Observer and ViewerCenterBoard.
    Author:
    Ali Arfan, Kent Erlend Bratteng Knudsen, Stian Tornholm Grimsgaard
